<p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Calculate sin œÜ‚ÇÇ</p>
<p>$\\sin\\phi_2 = \\sqrt{1 - \\cos^2\\phi_2} = \\sqrt{1 - 0.8^2} = \\sqrt{1 - 0.64} = \\sqrt{0.36} = 0.6$</p>
<p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Calculate per-unit voltage drop</p>
